<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 10:07:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>联合国：以色列的加沙撤离令可能违反国际法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-gaza-evacuation-order-could-breach-international-law-un/articleshow/104494931.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494931.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国人权办公室表示担心，以色列对加沙的围困及其飞地北部的疏散令可能构成强制转移平民，这将违反国际法。该办公室表示，以色列没有做出足够的努力，为撤离的平民提供适当的住宿、卫生、健康、安全和营养。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:50:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israels-gaza-evacuation-order-could-breach-international-law-un/articleshow/104494931.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩发射反坦克导弹后，黎以边境再次爆发冲突</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/clashes-again-erupt-on-the-lebanon-israel-border-after-an-anti-tank-missile-is-fired-from-lebanon/articleshow/104494601.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494601.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周二，黎巴嫩和以色列边境再次爆发冲突，自最近加沙战争爆发以来，以色列军队和黎巴嫩武装团体发生了一系列小规模冲突。据萨法德齐夫医疗中心称，周二上午，一枚从黎巴嫩发射的反坦克导弹落在以色列北部的梅图拉镇，造成三人受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:39:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/clashes-again-erupt-on-the-lebanon-israel-border-after-an-anti-tank-missile-is-fired-from-lebanon/articleshow/104494601.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普介入以色列对哈马斯的战争，誓言禁止加沙难民进入美国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-weighs-in-on-israels-war-on-hamas-vows-to-ban-gaza-refugees-from-entering-us/articleshow/104494710.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494710.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将把对难民的冻结扩大到包括来自加沙的人。他表达了反移民立场，并提出了各种限制移民和难民数量的政策。特朗普还发誓要禁止来自世界某些地区的个人，特别是信奉伊斯兰教的地区，并提议根据移民的意识形态来筛选移民。他没有提供有关如何执行此类筛查的详细信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-weighs-in-on-israels-war-on-hamas-vows-to-ban-gaza-refugees-from-entering-us/articleshow/104494710.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登前往以色列和约旦，重点关注地面进攻和人道主义危机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-heading-to-israel-and-jordan-focused-on-ground-offensive-and-humanitarian-crisis/articleshow/104494425.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104494425.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登即将前往以色列和约旦，评估以色列在与哈马斯冲突中的目标，并强调向加沙提供人道主义援助的重要性。访问期间，拜登将与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡以及约旦、埃及和巴勒斯坦领导人会面。此行的目的是表达对以色列的声援，同时避免更广泛的地区战争并解决加沙的人道主义危机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-heading-to-israel-and-jordan-focused-on-ground-offensive-and-humanitarian-crisis/articleshow/104494425.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在会谈中宣扬与智利的密切关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-jinping-touts-close-relationship-with-chile-in-talks/articleshow/104493915.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104493915.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国国家主席习近平周二在北京会见智利总统博里奇时表示，智利始终走在中国同拉美和加勒比国家关系前列。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 09:20:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinas-xi-jinping-touts-close-relationship-with-chile-in-talks/articleshow/104493915.cms</guid></item><item><title>“咄咄逼人”的中国战斗机惊扰了加拿大飞机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/aggressive-chinese-fighter-jets-spook-canadian-plane-on-un-mission/articleshow/104491668.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104491668.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名加拿大将军批评中国空军对中国海岸附近的加拿大侦察机采取攻击性和不安全的行为。这起事件涉及一架中国战斗机拦截巡逻机，向其飞行路径投掷照明弹，并在距飞机5米范围内飞行。中国就此事件向加拿大提出外交申诉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 08:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/aggressive-chinese-fighter-jets-spook-canadian-plane-on-un-mission/articleshow/104491668.cms</guid></item><item><title>议长：俄罗斯将撤销对禁止核试验条约的批准</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-is-revoking-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty-parliament-speaker/articleshow/104485973.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104485973.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯议会议长表示，由于美国对全球安全采取不负责任的态度，俄罗斯将撤回对《全面禁止核试验条约》的批准。弗拉基米尔·普京总统此前曾建议撤销批准，因为美国尚未批准该条约。俄罗斯仍将是禁试条约签署国，并将继续与禁试条约组织和全球监测系统合作。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 05:16:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-is-revoking-ratification-of-nuclear-test-ban-treaty-parliament-speaker/articleshow/104485973.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我是真主的战士”：受伊斯兰国启发的枪手在布鲁塞尔杀死了两名瑞典人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/i-am-fighter-for-allah-isis-inspired-gunman-kills-2-swedes-in-brussels/articleshow/104484105.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104484105.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名自称效忠伊斯兰国的枪手在布鲁塞尔杀害了两人，比利时警方在全市范围内展开搜捕。在比利时对阵瑞典的 2024 年欧洲杯预选赛之前，袭击者在伊普尔大道附近向一群瑞典球迷开枪，该大道距离该市著名的大广场以北仅几分钟路程。旁观者拍摄的令人不安的视频显示，袭击者骑着摩托车在公共场合跟踪并向人们开枪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 04:08:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/i-am-fighter-for-allah-isis-inspired-gunman-kills-2-swedes-in-brussels/articleshow/104484105.cms</guid></item><item><title>经过十年的大项目和巨额债务，中国的“一带一路”正在发生怎样的变化</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/how-chinas-belt-and-road-initiative-is-changing-after-a-decade-of-big-projects-and-big-debts/articleshow/104484292.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104484292.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着中国寻求解决债务和环境问题，中国的“一带一路”倡议将变得更小、更环保。 “一带一路”倡议旨在促进贸易、深化中国的全球关系，带动了全球重大基础设施项目的建设。然而，这一举措也导致了巨额债务和环境批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 04:02:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/how-chinas-belt-and-road-initiative-is-changing-after-a-decade-of-big-projects-and-big-debts/articleshow/104484292.cms</guid></item><item><title>习近平对弗拉基米尔·普京的赌博会得到回报吗？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-russia-relations-will-xi-jinpings-gamble-on-vladimir-putin-pay-off/articleshow/104484083.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104484083.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京抵达北京与中国国家主席习近平举行会晤。由于西方制裁，俄罗斯越来越依赖中国的贸易和经济支持，预计两位领导人将讨论两国不断发展的经济关系。然而，有人担心中国没有从两国关系中获得足够的利益，而普京正在成为习近平的负担。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 03:54:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-russia-relations-will-xi-jinpings-gamble-on-vladimir-putin-pay-off/articleshow/104484083.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京与内塔尼亚胡通话，誓言采取措施防止冲突升级</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/putin-speaks-to-netanyahu-about-gaza-conflict-promises-measures-to-prevent-escalation/articleshow/104483459.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104483459.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡就以色列-哈马斯战争进行了交谈，讨论了俄罗斯为防止加沙地带暴力进一步升级而采取的措施。普京向内塔尼亚胡通报了他与该地区和巴勒斯坦权力机构领导人会谈的情况。他向遇难以色列人家属表示哀悼，并强调俄罗斯希望通过政治和外交手段实现和平解决。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 03:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/putin-speaks-to-netanyahu-about-gaza-conflict-promises-measures-to-prevent-escalation/articleshow/104483459.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登将于周三访问以色列；伊朗发出警告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-to-visit-israel-on-wednesday-iran-issues-warning/articleshow/104481200.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481200.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，美国总统拜登将访问以色列，与以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡举行会谈，并表示支持以色列自卫权。预计以色列将对加沙发动地面攻击，以对抗哈马斯运动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-to-visit-israel-on-wednesday-iran-issues-warning/articleshow/104481200.cms</guid></item><item><title>康奈尔大学教授称哈马斯恐怖袭击“令人振奋”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/cornell-university-professor-calls-hamas-terror-attack-exhilarating-and-exciting/articleshow/104482832.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104482832.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;康奈尔大学教授拉塞尔·里克福德称哈马斯对以色列的袭击“令人振奋”和“振奋人心”。他声称这改变了政治平衡，打破了以色列不可战胜的幻想。里克福德认为，认识到这一转变的影响并不需要支持哈马斯。与此同时，在加沙紧张局势升级和人道主义危机之际，美国总统乔·拜登将访问以色列。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 03:02:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/cornell-university-professor-calls-hamas-terror-attack-exhilarating-and-exciting/articleshow/104482832.cms</guid></item><item><title>泰勒·斯威夫特的保安飞回以色列与哈马斯作战</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-security-guard-flies-back-to-israel-to-join-idf-and-fight-hamas/articleshow/104483268.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104483268.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在泰勒·斯威夫特 Eras 巡演期间保护她的一名保安已返回以色列，加入以色列国防军预备队。这名不愿透露姓名的警卫对哈马斯对以色列公民的袭击深感担忧。他在脸书上发布了一张自己穿着制服的照片，表达了对以色列的声援，并强调了维护人性的必要性。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 03:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-security-guard-flies-back-to-israel-to-join-idf-and-fight-hamas/articleshow/104483268.cms</guid></item><item><title>一带一路：普京访华会见“亲爱的朋友”习近平</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/belt-and-road-summit-vladimir-putin-xi-jinping-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/104482124.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104482124.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统普京抵达北京与中国国家主席习近平举行会晤。普京此访恰逢中国提出“一带一路”倡议10周年，该倡议因给各国带来债务负担而受到批评。两国领导人都从他们的联盟中受益，中国为俄罗斯提供经济支持，俄罗斯则充当对抗西方的堡垒。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 02:37:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/belt-and-road-summit-vladimir-putin-xi-jinping-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/104482124.cms</guid></item><item><title>被称为“邪恶面孔”的哈马斯加沙首领位列以色列目标名单之首</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dubbed-face-of-evil-hamas-gaza-chief-at-top-of-israels-target-list/articleshow/104481151.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481151.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔被认为是以色列军队计划入侵该飞地的首要目标。辛瓦尔在以色列监狱中服刑二十多年，于 2011 年获释。他被视为哈马斯内部的残暴执法者和以色列的死敌。据信他是最近造成 1,300 多名以色列人死亡的袭击事件的幕后黑手。辛瓦尔在汗尤尼斯长大，并于 1987 年帮助组建了哈马斯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 00:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/dubbed-face-of-evil-hamas-gaza-chief-at-top-of-israels-target-list/articleshow/104481151.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列：哈马斯有199名人质，高于此前估计</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-has-199-hostages-higher-than-previously-estimated/articleshow/104481293.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481293.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军方目前报告称，已有 199 人被哈马斯劫持为人质，这一数字较以色列高级军事官员上周提供的至少 150 名人质的初步估计有所增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-has-199-hostages-higher-than-previously-estimated/articleshow/104481293.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京将于周三在中国会见习近平并举行会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-to-meet-xi-for-talks-in-china-on-wed/articleshow/104481496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京计划在北京举行的纪念中国“一带一路”倡议十周年论坛上会见中国领导人习近平。此外，普京在接受采访时强调，金砖国家在人口购买力平价方面已经超越了七国集团国家，并强调该集团作为西方主导的国际机构的替代方案的潜在好处。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-to-meet-xi-for-talks-in-china-on-wed/articleshow/104481496.cms</guid></item><item><title>强硬派共和党人竞选美国众议院议长获得支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hardline-republican-jim-jordan-picks-up-support-in-bid-for-us-house-speaker/articleshow/104481454.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481454.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;强硬派共和党人吉姆·乔丹的美国众议院议长竞选活动正在赢得支持。尽管遭到本党内部的反对，乔丹相信他有动力赢得周二的投票。共和党的内讧推迟了对联邦机构的资助以及对以色列和乌克兰的援助。约旦承诺优先考虑军事和支出立法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hardline-republican-jim-jordan-picks-up-support-in-bid-for-us-house-speaker/articleshow/104481454.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国寻求联合援助乌克兰和以色列</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-seeks-to-club-ukraine-and-israel-aid/articleshow/104481238.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104481238.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府正在寻求国会批准一项紧急援助计划，其中包括对乌克兰的援助和对以色列的持续支持。这一战略承认这两场冲突的紧迫性，旨在通过将乌克兰与对以色列的援助联系起来，获得共和党对乌克兰的支持。此前，国会曾允许乌克兰的紧急资金失效。</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Oct 2023 01:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-seeks-to-club-ukraine-and-israel-aid/articleshow/104481238.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>